commit.message: we now use only Boost.Math from Boost

boost::shared_ptr -> std::shared_ptr

and add missing headers
replace boost::scoped_ptr and auto_ptr with std::unique_ptr

require xylib == 1.6

and update zlib download link

remove wxALIGN* flags that had no effect

spotted thanks to new wx sizer asserts

- use vector<double> instead of vector<Point> in root/background.*
- return the second half of working_space
